de.tud.kom.p2psim.overlay.bt
Class BTDataStore

java.lang.Object
  de.tud.kom.p2psim.overlay.bt.BTDataStore

public class BTDataStore
extends java.lang.Object

This class can be used for storing all kinds of data. Currently it is used for storing data that are used in different classes in the BitTorrent implementation. It additionaly stores the classes of the stored data. This can be used for ensuring data safety when casting.

Author:
Jan Stolzenburg
